<subSubSection pageId="4" pageNumber="23" type="disussion">
<paragraph blockId="4.[1983,2576,286,710]" pageId="4" pageNumber="23">This species is known from very few specimens and only four localities west of the Star (= Jayawijaya) Mountains. A population previously allocated to this species from near the Baliem Valley (Bokondini) may well be a distinct species. Two subspecies recognized.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
