</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="4" pageNumber="23" type="activity">
<paragraph blockId="4.[1369,2576,720,1459]" pageId="4" pageNumber="23">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1369,1608,1114,1143]" pageId="4" pageNumber="23">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
Limited observations of Weyland Ring-tailed Possums suggest they are very agile and active, even during the day.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
