</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="4" pageNumber="23" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="4.[1369,2576,720,1459]" pageId="4" pageNumber="23">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1371,1726,1267,1300]" pageId="4" pageNumber="23">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Least Concern on The IUCN Red List. The impact of hunting on the Weyland Ring-tailed Possum needs to be studied because it could rapidly become threatened if either human encroachment or hunting were to increase significantly.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
